reviewText: Quality Merchandise, Good Communication, Fast Shipping Great Music and Show
Got this as a birthday gift from a close friend.
not as good as his other productions

This is a compilation of selections from previous concerts in Italy, Venice and New York. This is highly recommended for those who don't already have a large Andre Rieu collection. A nice collection at a reasonable price.
If you love Andre Rieu which I do, & the sound of the violin!  This DVD is for you!
